query:
SELECT
                        a.id,
                        s.name,
                        s.cost,
                        s.class,
                        s.base
                    FROM
                        garage_addons a
                    INNER JOIN
                        garage_shop s
                    ON
                        s.id = a.id
                    WHERE
                        s.base = (SELECT v.id FROM garage_vehicles v WHERE v.plate = $1)
                        AND a.count > 0
